    <abstract>
      <t>Color is a 32-bit numerical attribute that is used to associate a
   Traffic Engineering (TE) tunnel or policy with an intent or objective
   (e.g. low latency).  This document specifies extensions to Path
   Computation Element Protocol (PCEP) to carry the color attribute.</t>
    </abstract>
